  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This Study investigates presence of preclinical atherosclerosis in patients with Juvenile
      Mixed Connective Tissue Disease in Norway.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      Patients and controls are examined with carotid ultrasound, venous blood is drawn, and they
      undergo a clinical examination.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
